snippet.title: ExoCorps Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Jetpack Deathmatch!  ExoCorps is a fast paced multiplayer FPS coming soon to Steam Early Access.  
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/368040/ExoCorps/
Website - https://exocorpsgame.com/

Fight your opponents over several square kilometers using high powered weapons and a full-flight jetpack.  Manage your power usage and detect-ability to gain the advantage in cat-and-mouse hunts and fierce dogfights.
